usage: main.py multiscale-anomaly [-h] --temperature TEMPERATURE [--mask MASK]
                                  [--no-mask] [--results RESULTS]
                                  [--step STEP] [--top TOP]

options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --temperature TEMPERATURE
                        Path to .npy file with temperature map
  --mask MASK           Path to .npy file with mask (omit or use --no-mask for
                        no mask)
  --no-mask             Do not use any mask (analyze all pixels)
  --results RESULTS     Path to output CSV file
  --step STEP           Step in degrees for grid (default: 5)
  --top TOP             Number of top anomalies to visualize (default: 20)
